Finally, my ultimate creation is complete: The Tennis-Tron X35-Z! It is the greatest tennis-playing robot in the WORLD! Now all I need is a tennis racket so that I can test him out! If you find one for me I will give you my hammer!
At last! A tennis-racket with which to test my creation! Here, you can have my hammer because I do not need it anymore!
Soon, the world will marvel at my new Tennis-Tron X35-Z. Just you wait and see!
No tennis racket here!
Duckies! Duckies! I wanna see the duckies! Have YOU seen the duckies!?!?! Take me to the DUCKIES!!!

You make me feel like dancin'!
Burn, baby, burn! Disco Inferno!
Someone must move this bus first before you can enter the resort.
Oh Phooey! I lost the keys to the bus somewhere around here! Help me find them and I will move it so that you can get into the resort!
Ah-ha! You found the keys! Excellent, I'll move the bus now! Have fun!
move me!

This bus is blocking the entrance to the resort!
WASH ME!

Uh-Oh! Somebody stole all of the water out of the pool and everyone is very anxious to go swimming! It is up to you to get into the pump-house and help Buttercup fill the pool again. You must find the wrench in order to start the water, but you may also want to gather other items along the way to help you fix the rusty pipes in that pump-house!
Good Luck!

Pool:
Straight Ahead
You there! Go and get me a first aid kit. I injured my head trying to jump into the pool that has no water. Quickly, GO NOW!
Much thanks. You may have this band-aid from the kit, for it is something that I do not need and therefore do not wish to possess!
Mojo-Jojo feels much better now.
Shave and a hair-cut... two bits!
Maybe I should move to a new house.....

Sorry! No more umbrellas today!

Alright! You found the wrench! Now let's go inside and try to get the pool filled up!
